# 🐾 Pets Assistant

A warm, conversational veterinary behavior assistant built with Streamlit and OpenAI.  
“Pets Assistant” guides cat owners through a structured interview, gathering detailed behavioral information for a veterinary visit.

---

## 🚀 Features

- **Interactive Q&A** – Asks 10 core questions in a friendly, natural flow.  
- **Empathetic Follow-Ups** – After each answer, prompts one intelligent, context-aware follow-up.  
- **One-Paragraph Clinical Summary** – At the end, generates a concise summary ready for your vet.  
- **Streamlit UI** – Slick chat interface with custom CSS “speech bubbles” and avatar emoji.  
- **Extensible** – Add your own tools via `@function_tool` or swap in a different model.

---

## 💻 Installation

1. **Clone the repo**  
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/pets-assistant.git
   cd pets-assistant
